## Verifies that the built-in `+` stratum (defined in src/strata/operators.si
## via the unified `@stratum Plus := { ... }; @fn Plus_lower ...` form) is
## correctly registered and dispatches `1 + 2` to i32.add at codegen time.
## The legacy `@stratum_operator Plus ('+', Node) = { ... }` form was retired
## as part of the Phase 5 grammar revision pass.
1 + 2;
